{
  "stem": "21354.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are now talking when I was 12, 13.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My greatest wish for my bar mitzvah is to have a radio.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And eventually I did have a crystal set, which is unknown to our children today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a crystal set where you had to twiddle to get a station, and you listened with earphones.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember one was most concerned because I was just about to leave school to go into a gymnasium, which was a higher education.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And whilst we set our tests, we were rejected, being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we returned to our basic school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One did hear, because we had a infamous concentration camp near Munich-- it was Dachau-- and anybody who didn't toe the line, Jews and non-Jews, went there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there were other cases.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Besides religious, there were political, criminal cases.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were all dispatched to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We are now talking '33, '34, '35.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My first experience was in Munich, when a young solicitor-- Jewish solicitor-- known to my parents, was marched through the town with a big placard around his neck-- I'm a Jew, I had committed something, something.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was promptly sent to Dachau, and returned very soon after in a leaded coffin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at that time, anybody killed in a concentration camp was returned to the Jewish community for burial in Munich.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, some returned alive, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember life became-- becoming very uncertain and very unsettled, and my parents made every strenuous effort to emigrate.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nobody would have us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So eventually we did obtain an affidavit to go to United States.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we prepared for immigration.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was now going on for '30-- 1937.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Suitcases were packed, everything was ready for immigration.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
